## Legal & Ethical Notice

This tool is **strictly for use in authorized security assessments** where explicit written permission is granted.
Unauthorized use of this tool, including but not limited to unauthorized surveillance, credential harvesting, or persistence installation, is **illegal** and unethical.
Use responsibly and always within your legal scope.

